    "description": "CrowdWorks Inc. provides Internet services for crowdsourcing in Japan. The company operates CrowdWorks, a crowdsourcing platform that connects companies with individuals over the Internet enabling orders to be placed and accepted for work; and management support services. It also offers TechDirect, a matching platform that offers high-skilled IT personnel; CrowsLinks, a specialized side job/second business matching service for high-value professionals; CrowdLog, a cloud-based man-hours and project management tool that collects employee man-hours and visualizes how companies work; and Human & Human, an organizational analysis tool specialized in the aggregation and analysis of employee data. In addition, the company provides a job matching registration service for IT freelancers; an AI tool to generate images and articles with sensible operations; an AI offline learning school; online school for side hustles and freelancers; PARK, an EC creation service; MemberPay, a payment service that allows online sales of fixed monthly fees and one-time services with no initial or monthly fees; and online community for freelancers and secondary jobs. CrowdWorks Inc. was incorporated in 2011 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan."
